    {
      "description": "ch0303_cafe_monolog_1",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "最凉快的地方是哪里呢……",
      "text_original": "一番涼しいのはどこだろう……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_cafe_monolog_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_cafe_monolog_2",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "亲睦会……好期待。",
      "text_original": "親睦会……楽しみ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_cafe_monolog_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_cafe_monolog_3",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "想拿出些委员长该有的样子呢……",
