    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_commonskill",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "一决胜负。",
      "text_original": "真剣勝負。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_commonskill.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "祭典，真热闹呢。连我都要兴奋起来了",
      "text_original": "お祭り、大盛り上がりだね。こっちまで熱くなってくる。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "阳照好强……得好好做好防晒才行。听说晒伤其实就是烧伤。",
      "text_original": "日差しが強い……ちゃんと紫外線対策しないと。日焼けって火傷なんだって。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlobby_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "您……很在意我吗？抱歉，我太引人注目了。",
      "text_original": "私が……気になるの？ごめんなさい、目立ってしまって……",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlobby_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "在祭典上吃的烤鸡串，总觉得有种特别的感觉。老师您不这么觉得吗？",
      "text_original": "お祭りで食べる焼き鳥って、特別な感じがする……先生もそう思わない？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "老师会一直看着我们大显身手直到最后的，对吧？",
      "text_original": "先生、私たちの活躍を見届けてくれる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "呵呵，迄今为止一直封印着的力量。现在展示给你看。",
      "text_original": "ふふっ、今まで封じてた力、見せてあげる。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlogin_season_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "虽然还有余力，但也不能松懈哦。",
      "text_original": "まだ余裕はあるけど、気を抜かずにいこう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlogin_season_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlogin_season_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "到最后冲刺阶段了呢，大家加油。",
      "text_original": "ラストスパートだね。みんな頑張ろう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlogin_season_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_eventlogin_season_end",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "老师，谢谢你陪我们到最后。下次也一起度过吧。",
      "text_original": "先生、最後までありがとう。次も一緒に楽しもうね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_eventlogin_season_end.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_exskill_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "这就是夏日的大海……",
      "text_original": "これが夏の海……。",
