    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_exskill_level_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "是不是有点太耀眼了？",
      "text_original": "眩しかったかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_exskill_level_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_exskill_level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "有点闪耀过头了呢。",
      "text_original": "輝きすぎちゃったかな。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_exskill_level_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_exskill_level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "我没有刻意这么做的啦……",
      "text_original": "狙ったわけじゃないんだけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_exskill_level_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_exweapon_get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我还有许多不足之处。即便如此，我还是想继续握着百莲。这并不是为了扮演百花缭乱的委员长，而是为了直面自己的内心。",
      "text_original": "私はまだまだ足りないことだらけ。それでも、この百蓮を持ち続けたいと思う。それは……百花繚乱の委員長を演じるためじゃない。――自分自身の心と向き合うために。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_exweapon_get.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "嗯，百莲也带上了哟。",
      "text_original": "うん、百蓮も持ったよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "右手，已经没问题了。交给我吧。",
      "text_original": "右腕、今なら大丈夫。任せて。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "如果老师想这么做的话……我会遵从。",
      "text_original": "先生がそうしたいなら……従うよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "难得来到海边……我想和大家一起留下难忘的回忆。老师也愿意……陪我一起吗？",
      "text_original": "こうして海に来たんだもの……みんなと忘れられない思い出を作りたいんだ。先生も、一緒に……付き合ってくれる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_gachaget.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "这样一来……右臂的封印又解开了一层。",
      "text_original": "これで……右腕の封印が1つ解けた。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "原来如此。我也还有成长的空间呢。",
      "text_original": "そっか。私にもまだ伸びしろがあったんだね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "让你见识一下……我从黄昏之中夺回的力量。",
      "text_original": "黄昏から取り戻した、私の力……見せてあげる。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉就像花苞绽放了一样。谢谢你，这都是老师的功劳。",
      "text_original": "つぼみが開いたような感じがする。ありがとう、先生のおかげだよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这个……怎样？",
      "text_original": "これ……どう、かな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "适合我的泳装比想象中还难找到呢……",
      "text_original": "思ったより似合う水着が見つからなくて……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "选择白色的理由吗……？",
      "text_original": "白を選んだ理由……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "因为大家都说这一套比较好看……",
      "text_original": "これが良いって、みんなに言われたから……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "护肤的秘诀？",
      "text_original": "スキンケアの秘訣？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "倒也没做什么特别的事情……",
      "text_original": "別に特別なことをしているわけじゃないんだけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊，说不定是烤鸟串的功劳？",
      "text_original": "あ。もしかしたら焼き鳥のおかげかも？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "人们常说，失去了才知道珍惜。",
      "text_original": "大切なものは失ってから気づくって、よく言うよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我也是这样。所以——",
      "text_original": "私もそうだった。だから――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我不会再放手了。绝对。",
      "text_original": "もう手放さない。絶対に。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "自从右臂被黄昏吞噬之后，我便忘记了依靠他人的方法。",
      "text_original": "右腕が黄昏に呑まれてから、私は誰かの手にすがることを忘れてしまった。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "所以总是一个人思考，试图只靠自己解决一切。",
      "text_original": "だからいつも一人で考えて、全部自分で解決しようとしてた。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……但是，现在不一样了。因为有老师和大家在。",
      "text_original": "……だけど、今は違う。先生とみんながいるから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "今后也……请多关照。",
      "text_original": "これからも……よろしくね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_login_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "欢迎回来，老师。希望今天也能帮上你的忙。",
      "text_original": "おかえり、先生。今日もお役に立てたらいいな。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_login_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_login_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊……我一直在等您。要去海边对吧？我已经换好衣服了。",
      "text_original": "あ……待ってたよ。海に行くんだよね？もう着替えておいたよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_login_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "一开始先按这个战术来吧。",
      "text_original": "最初はこの作戦でいこう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "对方应该从开局就会全力进攻。",
      "text_original": "向こうは序盤から全力で来るだろうから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……老师？有好好看我的手势吗？",
      "text_original": "……先生？私のサイン、ちゃんと見てる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "一开始就分心，可真不像老师呢。",
      "text_original": "最初からよそ見をするなんて、らしくないね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_2_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "到底是在看什……",
      "text_original": "一体何を見て……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_2_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊……原来如此。对不起。",
      "text_original": "あ……そっか。ごめんなさい。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这样反而没办法集中注意力呢。毕竟我……是个充满神秘感的美少女嘛。",
      "text_original": "逆に集中できないよね。私が……ミステリアスな美少女だから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "但是沙滩排球就是要这样打手势的……",
      "text_original": "ビーチバレーはこうやってサインを出すんだけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "现在开始换个方式会不会比较好呢？",
      "text_original": "今からでも、やり方を変えたほうがいいかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……不行吗，果然临时还是太晚了呢。",
      "text_original": "……ダメか、流石に遅いよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_6_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "就这样继续吧，老师。",
      "text_original": "このままいこう、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_6_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_6_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "只要是我们的话……一定没问题。",
      "text_original": "私たちなら……大丈夫。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_6_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "就像冰雪消融后，春天终会到来一样……我那荒芜的内心，似乎也迎来了萌芽的时刻。",
      "text_original": "雪が解けたら、春が訪れるように……。荒れ果てた私の心にも、芽吹きの時が来たみたい。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "老师果然很温柔呢。我也希望有一天，能成为和老师一样的人。",
      "text_original": "やっぱり優しいね。私も、いつか先生みたいになりたいな。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感谢您一直相信着我。……我很依赖老师哦",
      "text_original": "いつも信じてくれてありがとう。……先生のこと、頼りにしてるよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "除了长得漂亮之外，我好像也没什么长处……这样的我，也可以待在老师身边吗……？",
      "text_original": "美人なこと以外、特に取り柄がないんだけど……先生のそばにいても……いいかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我觉得，自己生于冬天这件事一定有它的意义。",
      "text_original": "私が冬に生まれたのには意味があるんだと思う。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "就像跨越严寒，在和煦阳光下绽放的花朵一样……",
      "text_original": "冬の厳しさを越えて、麗らかな日の下に咲く花のように……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "希望有一天，我终能盛开绽放。",
      "text_original": "私もいつか、咲き誇りたいんだ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "有这样一个人，只要待在他身边就会感到安心。",
      "text_original": "そばにいるだけで安心できる人がいるんだ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "听说今天正是那个人的生日。所以为了能成为难忘的回忆，我特意打扮成这样来为他庆祝。",
      "text_original": "今日はその人の誕生日なんだって。だから思い出に残るように、この格好でお祝いするね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "生日快乐，老师。",
      "text_original": "お誕生日おめでとう、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "在今天这样的日子穿泳装……我这样只是穿了泳装而已吧？。这也算Cosplay吗？",
      "text_original": "今日みたいな日に水着……。私はただ水着を着ただけなのかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶，不是吗？Cosplay的世界还真是深奥呢……",
      "text_original": "え、違う？コスプレの世界って奥深いんだね……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_newyear_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐，老师。难得是新年，还是聊些积极阳光的话题比较好呢。",
      "text_original": "あけましておめでとう、先生。お正月くらいは明るい話がいいよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_newyear_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_newyear_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "所以虽然只是从外表开始……但我还是试着换上了更有朝气的打扮……",
      "text_original": "だから形からではあるんだけど……明るい気分になれる格好にしてみたんだ……",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_newyear_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我还挺耐寒的哦。你看，就算穿着泳装也完全没问题。",
      "text_original": "寒さには強いほうだよ。ほら、今も水着だけど平気。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊……今天是不是穿红色的衣服……会更好一些……？",
      "text_original": "あ……今日は赤い服の方が……良かった……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_defeat_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "果然，我根本不配当委员长……",
      "text_original": "やはり私に委員長なんて無理だったんだ……",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_defeat_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_defeat_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "对不起，我…… 真一无是处……",
      "text_original": "ごめんなさい、私…本当に取り柄が少なくて……",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_defeat_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_in_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "我要让大家知道，我究竟是谁。",
      "text_original": "私が誰なのか、みんなに伝えるの。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_in_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "由我带领大家走向胜利。",
      "text_original": "勝利へ導くね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_victory_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "如果能回应老师的期待，那就太好了。",
      "text_original": "先生の期待に応えられたなら、良かった。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_victory_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0303_tactic_victory_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "我已经……不再是谁的“替代品”了。",
      "text_original": "私はもう……誰かの「代わり」じゃない。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_tactic_victory_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH0303_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "蔚蓝……档案。",
      "text_original": "ブルー……アーカイブ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/CH0303_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
